reviews.text:
Sometimes, it doesn't take very long to analyze and judge a vape. This right here is a what if for me. What if someone made Zima the right way? This is a simple yet vibrant lemon lime with hops, made deliciously chilly.  An adult version of 7-Up. Yanno, Zima. This is ridiculously tasty, and could easily be an all day vape. Definitely a welcome palette  cleanser after tons of sweet fruits, tobaccos, bakeries, and so on. Just light, crisp, brisk, and refreshing, yet with enough nuance to go "Howdy. You won't be forgetting me."&#xD;
&#xD;
Digging the hell outta this stuff!
